These should not be visible (no red):
<embed hidden="yes" type='image/png' src='../../../../images/fail.gif'><embed src='../../../../images/green-2147483649x255.png' type='image/png'></embed></embed>

These should not be visible (no red):
<embed hidden src='../../../../images/fail.gif' type='image/png'></embed>
<embed hidden="" src='../../../../images/fail.gif' type='image/png'></embed>
<embed hidden="hidden" src='../../../../ihis embed should be visible (green box):
<embed hidden="yes" type='image/png'></embed></embed>

These should not be visible (no red):
<embed hidden src='../../../../images/fail.gif' type='image/png'></embed>
<embed hidden="" src='../../../../images/fail.gif' type='image/png'></embed>
<embed hidden="hidden" src='../../../../images/fail.gif' type='image/png'></embed>
<embed hidden="true" src='../../../../images/fail.gif' type='image/png'></embed>
